                    "body": "Using this example code I see no problems:\n\n{code}\n$filter = new Zend_Filter_StringTrim();\nvar_dump($filter->filter('\u0417\u0435\u043d\u0434'));\n{code}\n\nThis means that the StringTrim filter DOES work with cyrillic text.",
